freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: Well on March 1 I got the terrible metallic taste in my mouth and my tongue felt tingly and kind of numb at same time. Lasted 2 days.

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: I have hypertension that is usually controlled (around 118/78) with Metoprolol 25 mg once a day.  Today my blood pressure went up to 157/89 .  Called my physician and she said to continue current medication, and check if over the weekend.  Don't know if that is vaccine related.
No pain in arm any more. Tiredness gone. Stomach ache gone. BP Still elevated.
No. BP back in normal range.
